description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 58, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 174, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, Stringalong for South, and 8 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [174 Votes, Top 10% Score]
